casebody.data:
Tuesday, November 14, 1995

MOTION DOCKET

94-2622. State v. Otte.

Cuyahoga County, No. 64617. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for stay of execution pending disposition of his appeal by this court,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for stay be, and hereby is, granted.
